"'''Nobody's Perfect'''" was a [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] appearing in [[Star Wars Tales 20|''Star Wars Tales'' 20]].

==Plot summary==
Before their wedding. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin]] tells [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé]] some of the other sins he has done besides killing a [[Tusken Raider/Legends|Tusken Raider]] tribe. Those sins include:

Killing a colony of Desert Gnomes for giving him bad directions;

Beating up a homeless [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] for bumping into him;

Talking back to [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan]] and letting Obi-Wan take the blame for his mistakes;

Setting the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] on [[Fire/Legends|fire]], this killing at least six Jedi.

After telling Padmé his mistakes he says he would understand if she cancels the wedding. Her response is to ask which wedding dress he thinks she should go with, the white one or the light pastel one.

